{"version":"1.2","person":{"datePublished":"2023-12-13","name":"Visconte Guido Spinola","nameForms":[{"lang":"it","fullText":"Visconte Guido Spinola","parts":[{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Prefix","value":"Visconte"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Given","value":"Guido"},{"type":"http://gedcomx.org/Surname","value":"Spinola"}],"order":"EUROTYPIC"}],"gender":"Male","lifespan":"1120–1183","fullLifespan":"1120–1183","portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/ejo8k/thumb200s.jpg","@type":"ImageObject"},"memoryArtifacts":[{"memoryType":"DOCUMENT","url":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7770-125044-22459-10/dist.png?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","memoryUrl":"https://www.familysearch.org/photos/artifacts/171618491","thumbnailUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/dascloud/patron/v2/TH-7770-125044-22459-10/thumb200s.jpg?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","deepZoomUrl":"https://sg30p0.familysearch.org/service/records/storage/deepzoomcloud/dzpatron/v1/TH-7770-125044-22459-10/scale?ctx=ArtCtxPublic","@type":"ImageObject"}],"birthDate":"+1120","birthPlace":{"address":"Milano, Milano, Lombardia, Itália","geo":{"latitude":45.4652,"longitude":9.1907,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"deathDate":"+1183","deathPlace":{"address":"Milano, Lombardia, Itália","geo":{"latitude":45.5525,"longitude":9.2226,"@type":"GeoCoordinates"},"@type":"Place"},"userCertifiedLifeSummary":" \nPais\n \t\nRuggero VISCONTI, Signore di Massino, di Albizzate et di Besnate †1189/\nConseiller de justice (1172), podestat de Bergame (1189) \nCasamento(s) e filho(s)\nCasado com Alda . tiveram\nOberto SPINOLA †1183\n \nMeios irmãos e meias irmãs\nPelo lado de Ruggero VISCONTI, Signore di Massino, di Albizzate et di Besnate , falecido depois de 1189, Conseiller de justice (1172), podestat de Bergame (1189)\ncom Garizia GENEVE, nascida em 1147 - a Milano\nM Uberto VISCONTI, Signore di Massino, di Albizzate, di Besnate et di Cislago †1267/ Casado com Berta PIRONEVO\nAutor desta árvore : Peter BACHELIER (peter781)\nContactar\n                Une génération s'en va, une autre vient Il en est des hommes comme des feuilles d'un arbre, feuilles de l'olivier,  du laurier ou de tout arbre qui conserve toujours son manteau de verdure. Ainsi la terre porte les hommes, comme un de ces arbres porte des feuilles elle est couverte d'hommes dont les uns meurent, dont les autres naissent pour leurs succéder. L'arbre a toujours sa robe éclatante; mais vois au-dessous combien de feuilles sèches tu foules aux pieds.                       Saint-Augustin (psaume 101)\n\n\n           Descendance de Mathurin et Jacquine Seigneur et Dame des Moncréaux.\n\nArbre constitué : des documents de Roger B. (pochette rouge), Philippe Brest (Théophile B.), Pierre Yves B. (généalogie Le Maire), et Alain B. (mise à jour), des archives départementales de la Sarthe et du Maine et Loire, des généalogies des familles Touzet, Huez, Jaunay et Chambolle, et des bases Roglo et Pierfit. \n\nAscendance Darwinienne\nCurrently researching : John Doe\nHistoria\n\nNotez que les noms de personnages en italique sont des liens vers leurs fiches.\n","events":[{"name":"Birth","sources":"0","year":"1120","date":"1120","place":"Milano, Milano, Lombardia, Itália"},{"name":"Birth of Child","sources":"0","year":"1145","date":"1145","place":"Milano, Lombardia, Itália","age":"25","id":"L8Y3-RGZ"},{"name":"Death","sources":"0","year":"1183","date":"1183","place":"Milano, Lombardia, Itália","age":"63"}],"parent":[{"name":"Roger Consul Of Milan","gender":"Male","lifespan":"1100–1189","birthDate":"+1100","deathDate":"+1189-02-09","age":89,"@type":"Person","identifier":"9Q3Y-SFF","url":"https://ancestors.familysearch.org/en/9Q3Y-SFF/roger-consul-of-milan-1100-1189","published":true},{"name":"Garizia Geneve","gender":"Female","lifespan":"1147–1198","birthDate":"+1147","deathDate":"+1198-03-29","age":51,"portrait":{"url":"https://tree-portraits-pgp.familysearchcdn.org/dzjng/thumb